    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You and your eidolon share an empathic connection while you ride it.</p>\n<p>You gain a bonus on Ride checks equal to one-half your summoner level and you also gain Mounted Combat as a bonus feat when mounted on your eidolon.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>The eidolon must possess the mount evolution to take this evolution.</p>\n<p><strong>Usage</strong></p>\n<p>Add this feature to the summoner, add @Compendium[pf-content.pf-feats.tZO6hWGZu9MwbtLI]{Mounted Combat} as well, while riding.&nbsp;</p>",
